Package: LaSARS
Type: Package
Title: Explore and Control Response Style in Survey Responding
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Jess Grimmond, Guy Hawkins, Scott Brown, Quentin Gronau
Maintainer: Jess Grimmond <jess.grimmond@newcastle.edu.au>
Description: This module allows users apply the Latent State and Response Style (LaSARS) model over survey data using maximum likelihood estimation. In doing so, less-biased estimates of latent states can be obtained, alongside interpretable response style parameters. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: jmvcore (>= 0.8.5), R6, GGally, ggplot2
